  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa9">
<l>kīḻ vāṉam veḷḷeṉṟu erumai ciṟu vīṭu</l>
<l>mēyvāṉ parantaṉa kāṇ mikkuḷḷa piḷḷaikaḷum</l>
<l>pōvāṉ pōkiṉṟāraip pōkāmal kāttuṉṉaik</l>
<l>kūvuvāṉ vantu niṉṟōm kōtukalam uṭaiya</l>
<l>pāvāy eḻuntirāy pāṭip paṟai koṇṭu</l>
<l>māvāy piḷantāṉai mallarai māṭṭiya</l>
<l>tēvāti tēvaṉaic ceṉṟu nām cēvittāl</l>
<l>āvāveṉṟārāyntaruḷēlōrempāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O uncle’s daughter who sleep on the bed</l>
<l rend="indent">as lamps shine all around the mansion [studded with] pure gems,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the incense emits fragrance,</l>
<l>Do open the latch of the door [made of] gems!</l>
<l>O aunt, will you not wake her up? Is your daughter mute or deaf or asleep?</l>
<l>Is she kept under guard [or] caught in the spell of the great slumber?</l>
<l>[We] have sung all the many names, saying again and again,</l>
<l>‘the great Dark [Lord]! Mādhava! [The Lord] from Vaikuṇṭha!’</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
